{"word":"H2431 - חֵילָם - Chêylâm - khay-lawm' - Helam","slug":"H2431","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֵילָם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Chêylâm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khay-lawm'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Helam"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>חלאם חילם</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>chêylâm chêl'âm</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>khay-lawm'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Helam = \"stronghold\" <ol><li>a place east of the Jordan, west of the Euphrates, in Gilead, at which the Syrians under Hadarezer were defeated by David</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H2428\">H2428</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2342\">H2342</a>, <a href=\"#/H2344\">H2344</a>, <a href=\"#/H2426\">H2426</a>, <a href=\"#/H2427\">H2427</a>, <a href=\"#/H2430\">H2430</a>, <a href=\"#/H2432\">H2432</a>, <a href=\"#/H2473\">H2473</a>, <a href=\"#/H2479\">H2479</a>, <a href=\"#/H2497\">H2497</a>, <a href=\"#/H4234\">H4234</a>, <a href=\"#/H4246\">H4246</a>"}]}